<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">عنوان المخطوط:</span> خلق الأعمال <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
